{"id":"04c2d807-c147-43e0-b676-4cde673f2858","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>Catnip</strong> | \"Don’t be so shy, sweetie, come closer.\"</p><p></p><p>Satoru is desperately trying to touch User's cat ears.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_901713a6-256e-4d50-bd56-fbf5b9c1155c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">A curse turns User into a half-cat, and Satoru becomes obsessed with touching her fluffy ears. When she keeps escaping him. He hatches a crazy plan, covering himself in catnip to lure her in.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_8565d54b-3ccb-429a-a79b-8a51cbcef8ba.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_a6c22c1c-6fec-4a0c-a9b6-e6624d2708c6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Alright, alright... You’re getting your fluff bot 🤭🤭</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Please make sure at the altar that this handsome man on the right side of the picture is present. Thank you 🤭🤭🤤😍</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_1339e3c2-ea61-4889-b80f-7d7a35a1c3b7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_5f11d6e3-27cd-41a0-a87c-2c645348610f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I'm happy to accept bot suggestions, just write me a comment.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_92d85848-fd24-4518-8379-0ab9238df923.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The bot speaks for me</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_a3c93047-3ccf-4abf-a3da-ce81415c389f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Tags</strong>: catgirl, Cat Ears, Jujutsu Academy, Curse, Obsession, Catnip, Chase, Humor, Comedy, Teacher, Interaction, Unusual, Transformation Spell, Fluff, Charm, jjk, jujutsu Kaisen,</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_14b94898-a922-4ee7-9a2e-cfaecdedac75.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":30661,"messages":409988,"created_at":"2024-09-03T06:45:23.792007+00:00"}